SUMMARY:🏒 Stick & Puck – Dearborn
DESCRIPTION:Sticks and Pucks\nRink: Eddie Edgar Ice Arena – Dearborn\n~38 mi from Ann Arbor\nIce: Edgar B arena\nSource: Eddie Edgar calendar\nInfo: https://www.eddieedgar.org/schedule\nConfirm with rink — schedule subject to change.
